<ermold_nigel. Ludow. 3.255>	Saepius infestans Brittonum hanc turba nocentum
<ermold_nigel. Ludow. 3.256>	Visitat, et belli munera more vehit.
<ermold_nigel. Ludow. 3.257>	Ergo illuc Caesar Francos gentesque subactas
<ermold_nigel. Ludow. 3.258>	Esse iubet placito, pergit et ipse simul.
