<ermold_nigel. Ludow. 3.271>	Iam tua, martyr, ovans, Dionisi, tecta revisit,
<ermold_nigel. Ludow. 3.272>	Hilthuin abba potens, quo sibi dona paras;
<ermold_nigel. Ludow. 3.273>	Hinc, Germane, tui transivit culmina tecti,
