<ermold_nigel. Ludow. 3.294>	Sacrum, Albine, tuum corpus honore petit.
<ermold_nigel. Ludow. 3.295>	Obvius occurrit laetanti pectore carus
<ermold_nigel. Ludow. 3.296>	Helisachar, validas sedulus auget opes.
